PrecisJOINT CANADA-UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT PROJECTS REMISSION ORDER - which provides: (a) for the remission of various duties and taxes payable on goods, real property or services used in connection with certain joint Canada-U.S.government projects; and (b) the repeal of the remission granted under Part I of Order in Council P.C. 1960-1600 of Nov. 25, 1960.
